---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="FTL Propulsion Technology"
  description="Weyland-Yutani's proprietary faster-than-light drive systems enable interstellar transit across humanity's colonial network. Discovered 2032, first operational vessel launched 2034."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-black pt-36">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden scanlines border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20"></div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 py-24">
        <div class="max-w-5xl">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
            <a href="/technology" class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] hover:text-[#FFC600] transition-colors">TECHNOLOGY</a>
            <span class="text-gray-700">/</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">FTL PROPULSION</span>
          </div>

          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black text-white mb-6 leading-[0.9] uppercase">
            FTL<br/><span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">PROPULSION</span>
          </h1>

          <div class="h-1 w-48 bg-[#FFC600] mb-8"></div>

          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl uppercase tracking-wide font-mono leading-relaxed">
            PROPRIETARY FASTER-THAN-LIGHT DRIVE TECHNOLOGY ENABLING INTERSTELLAR TRANSIT. THE FOUNDATION OF HUMAN EXPANSION BEYOND SOL.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Metrics -->
    <section class="relative py-16 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-2">2032</div>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">PRINCIPLE DISCOVERED</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-2">2034</div>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">FIRST FTL VESSEL</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-2">1,200+</div>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">FTL-CAPABLE VESSELS</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-2">99.97%</div>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">TRANSIT SAFETY RATE</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Technical Overview -->
    <section class="relative py-32 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 max-w-7xl">
          <div>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">TECHNICAL OVERVIEW</div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-8 uppercase">BEYOND THE LIGHT BARRIER</h2>

            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              IN 2032, WEYLAND CORPORATION RESEARCHERS IDENTIFIED A PREVIOUSLY UNOBSERVED INVERSE RELATIONSHIP BETWEEN VELOCITY AND TIME AT SUPERLUMINAL THRESHOLDS. THIS DISCOVERY FUNDAMENTALLY ALTERED OUR UNDERSTANDING OF SPACETIME AND OPENED THE DOOR TO PRACTICAL INTERSTELLAR TRANSIT.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              WITHIN TWO YEARS, THE PRINCIPLE WAS ENGINEERED INTO A FUNCTIONAL PROPULSION SYSTEM. THE HELIADES, LAUNCHED IN 2034, BECAME THE FIRST FTL-CAPABLE EXPLORATION VEHICLE IN HUMAN HISTORY, VALIDATING DECADES OF THEORETICAL WORK AND USHERING IN THE ERA OF INTERSTELLAR TRAVEL.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              THE PROPRIETARY DRIVE CORE OPERATES ON A CLASSIFIED FIELD GEOMETRY THAT CREATES A LOCALIZED SPACETIME DISTORTION ENVELOPE AROUND THE VESSEL. WITHIN THIS ENVELOPE, THE CRAFT TRAVERSES INTERSTELLAR DISTANCES WITHOUT VIOLATING RELATIVISTIC CONSTRAINTS ON THE OCCUPANTS OR CARGO.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed">
              DRIVE SPECIFICATIONS AND CORE ARCHITECTURE REMAIN CLASSIFIED AT THE HIGHEST LEVELS OF CORPORATE SECURITY. ALL FTL SYSTEMS ARE MANUFACTURED EXCLUSIVELY AT WEYLAND-YUTANI SECURE FACILITIES AND ARE NOT AVAILABLE FOR THIRD-PARTY LICENSING.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="terminal">
              <div class="terminal-content">
                <div class="mb-6">
                  <span class="text-gray-500">// FTL DRIVE SYSTEM OVERVIEW</span>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-3 text-xs">
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> DRIVE TYPE: <span class="text-white">PROPRIETARY FIELD GEOMETRY</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> PRINCIPLE: <span class="text-white">INVERSE V/T RELATIONSHIP</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> FIRST OPERATIONAL: <span class="text-white">2034 (HELIADES)</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> POWER SOURCE: <span class="text-white">FUSION REACTOR ARRAY</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> TRANSIT SPEED: <span class="text-[#FF0000]">[CLASSIFIED]</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> MAX RANGE: <span class="text-[#FF0000]">[CLASSIFIED]</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> FIELD GEOMETRY: <span class="text-[#FF0000]">[CLASSIFIED]</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> CREW EXPOSURE: <span class="text-white">NOMINAL (ZERO RELATIVISTIC EFFECTS)</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> INTEGRATION: <span class="text-white">HYPERSLEEP COMPATIBLE</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> SAFETY RECORD: <span class="text-white">99.97% SUCCESSFUL TRANSITS</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> ACTIVE FLEET: <span class="text-white">1,200+ EQUIPPED VESSELS</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> MANUFACTURE: <span class="text-white">W-Y SECURE FACILITIES ONLY</span></div>
                  <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-[#FFC600]/20">
                    <span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> STATUS: <span class="text-[#FFC600]">OPERATIONAL / GEN-IV PRODUCTION</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Historical Timeline -->
    <section class="relative py-32 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-y-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
          <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">DEVELOPMENT HISTORY</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase">PROGRAM MILESTONES</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-4xl space-y-8">
          <div class="flex gap-8">
            <div class="w-20 shrink-0 text-right">
              <div class="text-lg font-black text-[#FFC600]">2032</div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l-2 border-[#FFC600] pl-8 pb-8">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">PRINCIPLE DISCOVERY</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
                WEYLAND CORP ADVANCED PHYSICS DIVISION IDENTIFIES THE INVERSE VELOCITY/TIME RELATIONSHIP AT SUPERLUMINAL THRESHOLDS. THEORETICAL FRAMEWORK VALIDATED THROUGH SUBATOMIC PARTICLE ACCELERATION EXPERIMENTS AT THE YUTANI COLLIDER COMPLEX, OSAKA.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-8">
            <div class="w-20 shrink-0 text-right">
              <div class="text-lg font-black text-[#FFC600]">2033</div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l-2 border-[#FFC600] pl-8 pb-8">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">PROTOTYPE DRIVE CORE</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
                FIRST FUNCTIONAL FTL DRIVE CORE ASSEMBLED AT WEYLAND ORBITAL RESEARCH STATION. UNMANNED TEST VEHICLE ACHIEVES SUPERLUMINAL TRANSIT IN CONTROLLED DEEP-SPACE ENVIRONMENT. RESULTS CLASSIFIED IMMEDIATELY.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-8">
            <div class="w-20 shrink-0 text-right">
              <div class="text-lg font-black text-[#FFC600]">2034</div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l-2 border-[#FFC600] pl-8 pb-8">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">HELIADES LAUNCH</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
                THE HELIADES, HUMANITY'S FIRST FTL-CAPABLE EXPLORATION VEHICLE, LAUNCHES FROM EARTH ORBIT. SUCCESSFUL TRANSIT TO ALPHA CENTAURI SYSTEM CONFIRMS COMMERCIAL VIABILITY. ERA OF INTERSTELLAR TRAVEL BEGINS.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-8">
            <div class="w-20 shrink-0 text-right">
              <div class="text-lg font-black text-[#FFC600]">2038</div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l-2 border-[#FFC600] pl-8 pb-8">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">GENERATION II DRIVES</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
                SECOND-GENERATION FTL DRIVES ENTER PRODUCTION. IMPROVED RANGE, REDUCED POWER REQUIREMENTS, AND ENHANCED SAFETY MARGINS. FIRST COLONY SHIPS EQUIPPED FOR LONG-RANGE INTERSTELLAR MISSIONS.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-8">
            <div class="w-20 shrink-0 text-right">
              <div class="text-lg font-black text-[#FFC600]">2050s</div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l-2 border-[#FFC600] pl-8 pb-8">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">FLEET STANDARDIZATION</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
                GENERATION III FTL SYSTEMS ADOPTED AS STANDARD ACROSS ALL WEYLAND-YUTANI COMMERCIAL, MILITARY, AND EXPLORATION VESSELS. USCM INTEGRATION AGREEMENTS SIGNED. TRANSIT NETWORK SPANS 100+ STAR SYSTEMS.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-8">
            <div class="w-20 shrink-0 text-right">
              <div class="text-lg font-black text-[#FFC600]">NOW</div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l-2 border-[#FFC600] pl-8">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">GENERATION IV PRODUCTION</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
                CURRENT-GENERATION FTL DRIVES FEATURE ENHANCED EFFICIENCY, MODULAR ARCHITECTURE, AND COMPATIBILITY WITH ALL MAJOR VESSEL CLASSES. OVER 1,200 FTL-EQUIPPED VESSELS IN ACTIVE SERVICE. GENERATION V RESEARCH UNDERWAY.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Applications -->
    <section class="relative py-32 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
          <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">FLEET APPLICATIONS</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase">DEPLOYMENT ACROSS ALL SECTORS</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-6xl">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">COLONY TRANSPORT</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
              LARGE-DISPLACEMENT COLONY VESSELS EQUIPPED WITH FTL DRIVES AND INTEGRATED HYPERSLEEP SYSTEMS. CAPABLE OF TRANSPORTING THOUSANDS OF COLONISTS AND MILLIONS OF TONS OF EQUIPMENT TO DISTANT STAR SYSTEMS.
            </p>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase">VESSEL CLASSES: CONESTOGA, BISON, HELIADES-C</div>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">MILITARY OPERATIONS</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
              RAPID-DEPLOYMENT TACTICAL VESSELS FOR USCM AND ALLIED MILITARY FORCES. FTL TRANSIT ENABLES FORCE PROJECTION ACROSS INTERSTELLAR DISTANCES WITH STRATEGIC RESPONSE TIMES.
            </p>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase">VESSEL CLASSES: CONESTOGA-CLASS, AURIGA-CLASS</div>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">COMMERCIAL TRANSPORT</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
              AUTOMATED AND CREWED FREIGHT VESSELS LINKING COLONIAL ECONOMIES. FTL-ENABLED SUPPLY CHAINS CONNECTING 300+ WORLDS WITH EARTH AND CORE-SYSTEM MANUFACTURING CENTERS.
            </p>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase">VESSEL CLASSES: NOSTROMO-CLASS, LOCKMART</div>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">DEEP SPACE EXPLORATION</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
              LONG-RANGE SURVEY AND SCIENCE VESSELS DESIGNED FOR MULTI-YEAR MISSIONS BEYOND THE ESTABLISHED COLONIAL NETWORK. EXTENDED-RANGE FTL DRIVES WITH ENHANCED NAVIGATIONAL SYSTEMS.
            </p>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase">VESSEL CLASSES: PROMETHEUS-CLASS, COVENANT-CLASS</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Hypersleep Integration -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-t-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">INTEGRATED SYSTEMS</div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase">HYPERSLEEP INTEGRATION</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              ALL FTL-EQUIPPED VESSELS INCORPORATE WEYLAND-YUTANI HYPERSLEEP SYSTEMS AS STANDARD. WHILE FTL TRANSIT DRAMATICALLY REDUCES INTERSTELLAR JOURNEY TIMES, VOYAGES SPANNING WEEKS OR MONTHS STILL BENEFIT FROM CREW STASIS TO CONSERVE LIFE SUPPORT RESOURCES AND MAINTAIN OPERATIONAL READINESS.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-8">
              THE INTEGRATION OF FTL PROPULSION AND HYPERSLEEP REPRESENTS THE COMPLETE SOLUTION FOR HUMAN INTERSTELLAR TRANSIT: FASTER TRAVEL BETWEEN STARS COMBINED WITH ZERO EFFECTIVE TRAVEL TIME FOR CREW AND PASSENGERS.
            </p>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <a href="/technology/hypersleep" class="btn-secondary text-sm">HYPERSLEEP TECHNOLOGY</a>
              <a href="/products/hypersleep-chambers" class="btn-secondary text-sm">VIEW PRODUCTS</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-6 pb-4 border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
              FTL + HYPERSLEEP SYSTEM INTEGRATION
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">&gt;</span>
                <span class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase">AUTOMATED STASIS INITIATION PRIOR TO FTL TRANSIT</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">&gt;</span>
                <span class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase">CONTINUOUS LIFE-SIGN MONITORING DURING TRANSIT</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">&gt;</span>
                <span class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase">SCHEDULED REVIVAL PROTOCOLS WITH SAFETY MARGINS</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">&gt;</span>
                <span class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase">EMERGENCY WAKE CAPABILITY AT ANY TRANSIT STAGE</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">&gt;</span>
                <span class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase">MUTHUR SHIPBOARD AI MANAGES ALL INTEGRATION SYSTEMS</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">&gt;</span>
                <span class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase">ZERO EFFECTIVE TRAVEL TIME FOR CREW AND PASSENGERS</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="relative py-20 bg-black border-t-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-2 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase">FTL SYSTEMS ARE AVAILABLE FOR AUTHORIZED PROCUREMENT</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          FTL DRIVE SYSTEMS ARE SUBJECT TO EXPORT CONTROLS AND REQUIRE SECURITY CLEARANCE FOR ACQUISITION. CONTACT OUR DEFENSE AND FLEET SOLUTIONS DIVISION FOR INQUIRIES.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">CONTACT FLEET SOLUTIONS</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .clip-corner {
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 8px);
  }
</style>
